      <title>Cities weren’t designed for cars. They were designed for people. In Copenhageniz...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DViTIzvCrI5/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DViTIzvCrI5/"><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/641363167_18563523820048695_6073503109078822418_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_s640x640_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=111&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg0NjcyMTE5OTkxNzQxMjkyMTE4NTYzNTIzODE3MDQ4Njk1.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjU0MHg5NjAuc2RyLkMzIn0%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=h7rEUo3AjhMQ7kNvwFQQvWf&amp;_nc_oc=AdpweUJ1IZwvpmA9RbTH9mbhZXePmckBGZOjQT19mHI81qPE-epYeuCfjp0MxU_FNY4&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=4kZUuAkZwXVY4DODEJQE7A&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_Afy3j8a07ZyYMEt1tkR3Qwu9eVdt4JYSGmTNi3Q6OIkIIg&amp;oe=69CA22DA" alt="Video-thumbnail fra @analogville.urbanism" /></a></p><p><strong>🎬 Video</strong></p><p><strong>@analogville.urbanism</strong></p><p>Cities weren’t designed for cars. They were designed for people.<br/>
In Copenhagenize, urban designer and TV host Mikael Colville-Andersen reveals how cities around the world can reclaim their streets by putting bicycles and human life first.<br/>
<br/>
Drawing on two decades of experience as an urban designer and bicycle planner, research, global case studies, and the everyday success of Copenhagen, the book shows how safe bike infrastructure, better street design, and human-scale planning can transform cities into healthier, happier places.<br/>
<br/>
The bicycle isn’t a lifestyle choice. It’s urban infrastructure.<br/>
<br/>
Available in bookshops and online. English, German, Polish (Byc Jak Kopenhaga) and Ukrainian (Копенгагенізація) <br/>
<br/>
#books #design #bikes #cycling #copenhagenize</p><p><a href="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t16/f2/m69/AQOqF3mfvJ4jdCUwzZYIM-asft67HjaJzuAvBoWz6kJLAInVfhTWUiUiBn_UbmgO-WKme-axewe-fDmHbdf_-h-k.mp4?strext=1&amp;_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_sid=5e9851&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_ohc=OadAHDvjSbUQ7kNvwEgVKrp&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6Inhwdl9wcm9ncmVzc2l2ZS5JTlNUQUdSQU0uQ0xJUFMuQzMuNzIwLmRhc2hfYmFzZWxpbmVfMV92MSIsInhwdl9hc3NldF9pZCI6MTc5NDYyNjgyMzMxMTg1OTQsImFzc2V0X2FnZV9kYXlzIjoxOSwidmlfdXNlY2FzZV9pZCI6MTAwOTksImR1cmF0aW9uX3MiOjY3LCJ1cmxnZW5fc291cmNlIjoid3d3In0%3D&amp;ccb=17-1&amp;vs=1a191af350a7a3e5&amp;_nc_&amp;_nc_gid=4kZUuAkZwXVY4DODEJQE7A&amp;_nc_zt=28&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfzSL7wBdFSJdFW3lFoxOMlcEpQCjJEtNLF0Nc7aDtY1UQ&amp;oe=69CA1DF4">▶️ Åbn video direkte</a> · <a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DViTIzvCrI5/">se på Instagram</a></p>]]></description>
